  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de GStreamer Bad Plug-ins</title>

    <para>
      Installez <application>GStreamer Bad Plug-ins</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes&nbsp;:
       
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr             --with-package-name="GStreamer Bad Plugins &gst10-plugins-bad-version; BLFS"             --with-package-origin="http://www.linuxfromscratch.org/blfs/view/svn/" &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Pour tester le résultat, tapez&nbsp;: <command>make check</command>.
    </para>

    <para>
      Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>
  </sect2>

